{"tid":2070010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根本好多外地回港確診個案，喺香港返到嚟傳染到的","createTime":"2020-06-18T23:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T02:15:05.000Z","uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b786877a8736a3d7ff8049164a4064b0754549c","tid":2070010,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T23:47:43.000Z","msg":"基本上返到嚟香港，你就喺機場轉去檢疫嘅地方，一搞搞你三個鐘，三個鐘只係做兩樣野，吐啖口水，同埋安排酒店。基本上搞完嗰三個鐘，你個人都開始病病地。<br />\n之後去酒店，酒店嗰啲房間根本係唔in service ,開咗冷氣都有浸味，係嗰種間房有好多年冇用過咁嘅狀態。影咗少少相keep record，但放上嚟驚犯法"},{"pid":"7cf306f57c1911ee6315b65dcbb33700737fc151","tid":2070010,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:15:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\">同我入嚟like 女拔 楊老師個page + 課金預訂佢本書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2070055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2070055</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</div><br />\n<br />\nFb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lc.ryeung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flc.ryeung%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=d2fbff69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lc.ryeung/</a><br />\n訂書 （有2 本）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/bookorder612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fbookorder612&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=0d3ab282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/bookorder612</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}